Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Alert all SDF platoons and battalions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that we have a class one\N{\c&He1e1e1&}emergency situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A class one emergency situation\N{\c&He1e1e1&}has been declared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All SDF units, please deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the 25th Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Blockade of SDF's front gate\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Blockade of North Gate 34 is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commander, blockade of the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}front entrance is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The intruder is currently\N{\c&He1e1e1&}escaping toward N Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Life and death... They are{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}two sides of the same future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Some people will die,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and some people will{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}go on living. However,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}those who go on living,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}while their friends die in front of them,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are sometimes called by a certain name...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}''Grim Reaper.''{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The intruder has been spotted\N{\c&He1e1e1&}currently passing through 2 Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Send everything we have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to apprehend the intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This isn't happening... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Life or Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Not again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This way, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry up with that blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, what is Yuuki's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Manabu!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- {\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I was attacked... by the intruder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He lost an awful lot of blood,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}but I've given him first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, what happened to the intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We still haven't captured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But it couldn't have gotten\N{\c&He1e1e1&}outside of SDF Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, David, Louis,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we're heading back to N Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're not coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}keep your eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm fine now. This wound is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}R- right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The intruder has been spotted.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}They're fighting it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Send backup at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Did we get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The backup squad has\N{\c&He1e1e1&}stopped transmitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Many determined lives are vanishing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Young people, take over for them,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and do not let their fire go out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I thought that Bruce\N{\c&He1e1e1&}had finally accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He is doing this because\N{\c&He1e1e1&}he has accepted you, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Back when {\i1}Owen-san{\i0} passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn... I blew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Owen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't worry... this isn't your fault...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm the one who was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't talk! Yuki will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I told you... I'm immortal, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just watch... I'll prove you're not...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the Grim Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Owen... Owen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This isn't happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Owen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"The Grim Reaper has not left me."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I remember him muttering that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ever since then, {\i1}Bruce-san{\i0} has tried\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to work alone. {\i1}Bruce-san{\i0} is afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...that he might lose his partner...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you, {\i1}Yuuki-san...{\i0} once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is why he behaves like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Grim Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-- san!{\i0} Don't strain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going, Yuki. If Bruce is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}trying to keep me at a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that's all the more reason\N{\c&He1e1e1&}why I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I have to go and put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The idea of it... Bruce is not the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Grim Reaper. I believe that to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Special Infiltration Team 8-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I have successfully\N{\c&He1e1e1&}acquired the top-secret data.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've been discovered,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and their defenses are activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Extrication is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An external communications terminal\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the 5th maintenance hangar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- has been activated!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Terminate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Increase security in the area\N{\c&He1e1e1&}around the 5th maintenance hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Calling all units! Please proceed to the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}area around the 5th maintenance hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Bruce. I've arrived\N{\c&He1e1e1&}at the 5th maintenance hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So this is where it was\N{\c&He1e1e1&}communicating from, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, I can't locate it\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the 5th maintenance hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood. I've just sent\N{\c&He1e1e1&}David and Louis to back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A large quantity of gas has been\N{\c&He1e1e1&}released into the 5th maintenance hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's nerve gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Underground personnel are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Seal off C Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have all underground personnel\N{\c&He1e1e1&}equip masks or helmets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Closing C Block blast doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Vents open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you hurt? Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You stupid ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David! David! Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why are you here, Manabu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can't I be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am your partner, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Never mind, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not leaving. I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You can't! Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm possessed by the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're just being superstitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Anyone that teams up with me\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is sure to die. That is my destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to change that destiny,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, are you sure you should be up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun,{\i0} are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take him back to where Yuki is for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What for? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, please let go of me!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not about to take someone\N{\c&He1e1e1&}who is injured with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You heard him, Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's Bruce the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You know what happens to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}those that team up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Grim Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can't tell you whether to go or stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Manabu, take care of Bruce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, we're going the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:12:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn... That gas from earlier\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is starting to kick in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Has the intruder been secured yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is currently heading toward B Block\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the Maintenance Floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Close hatch number 28 in B Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Closing hatch number 28 in B Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Five missing and three in critical\N{\c&He1e1e1&}condition from the 15th Maintenance Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}20% of the blast doors\N{\c&He1e1e1&}within the building are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}5% of the personnel within the building\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are wounded or in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I need some help over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Status report from Spica Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The intruder appears to be moving\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from Area 9 toward Area 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Did you copy that, David, Louis,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and Bruce? Move your search to Area 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Copy.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce! Respond, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll keep you informed\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as to what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, that's far enough!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Who are you!? What are you after!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Talk! What... are you after!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Talk! Start talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's you, is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce the Grim Reaper, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You know quite a bit about me,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am Owen the Immortal, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to bust you down\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from "Bruce the Grim Reaper"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}to just plain "Bruce."\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Owen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've just confirmed that the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}engine of the freight train {\i1}No. 531,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}parked in the 4th Maintenance Hangar,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}has started up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Close the blast door!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to kill you for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Come on!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Bruce!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you trying to get both\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you and that criminal killed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The SDF is not a death squadron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're the one who told me that, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to settle this between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not letting that thing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}take anyone else away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Look. Isn't that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No doubt about it. That's Bruce's rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Uh-huh. I sure hope nothing bad\N{\c&He1e1e1&}has happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah. I know I heard Yuuki contacting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I heard his transmission, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki is with Bruce, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, I should have stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're going in to locate those two,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and to secure the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}End of the line! All of the exits\N{\c&He1e1e1&}have been locked down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's put an end to this, Reaper!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Drop your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't do it, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Drop it, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right. I'll do as you say,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}just don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, it's like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not letting that thing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}take anyone else from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, what are you doing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David! David, is that you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Wandering around, all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Bruce-san,{\i0} aren't you lonesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you talking about, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, how come\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you're the only one alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, what are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain... Yuki... Louis... David...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}T- this can't be happening...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Painful, isn't it? Living with\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the burden of other people's deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}These memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't want to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}have them anymore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you rather die instead?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Like your friends did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You won't have to live\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with the guilt of surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Did you kill them!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am the one who killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, it's your fault.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Once you die, it will all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You want to feel better, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce! Get up! Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shoot the Grim Reaper!
